Infrastruture and cloud Automation

situation:the client lacked standardized cloud infrastructures and deplyments were inconsistent across enviromnets

task:
design and provison a scalable and repetble aws infrastructutre for the ecommerce plateform

action:
1. used terafor to provision aws infrastructure including EKS,ec2(jenkins and bastion),Iam roles and networking
2. implemented infrastructure as code to ensure consistency across environment
3. configured aws cli and kubeconfig access securely via bastion host 

results:
 1. reduced infrasture setup time from days to under an hour
 2  achieved reproducedble and version controlled infrasture
 3. improved environment relaiblilty and audaditabilty
 

ci pipeline impleented(jenkins)

situations: Application build and deplyments were manual,error-prone and not version-controlled.

Task:Implement Ci pipeline to automate build,test and container image creation.
action:
