2. designed jenkins pipeline using jenkins file and shared libraries
3. automated docker image build and push to docker hub with version taging
4. integerated github webhooks for automatic pipeline triggering.

results:
01. enable fully automated CI process.
02. reused deployment failures caused by manual steps.
03. improved release frequency and consistency

